response.overview: The hot-headed young D'Artagnan along with three former legendary but now down on their luck Musketeers must unite and defeat a beautiful double agent and her villainous employer from seizing the French throne and engulfing Europe in war.
response.tagline: Every legend has a new beginning.
response.title: The Three Musketeers

titles.title: Die drei Musketiere  - Alle für einen und Waffen für alle
